{"tid":2162614,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實生細路黎講，生仔真係high risk過生女好撚多","createTime":"2020-08-18T08:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T07:21:52.000Z","uid":58316,"like":16,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e68d7e495ddf47e693c4f1be8d38b617a612eb74","tid":2162614,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T08:16:29.000Z","msg":"有時諗<br />\n自己會唔會生細路<br />\n生女就由9得佢<br />\n穩賺不賠<br />\n零成本高回報<br />\n無本生利<br />\n但生仔<br />\n分分鐘十分耕耘<br />\n零分收穫<br />\n但唔理佢又唔得<br />\n理<br />\n又唔理得咁多<br />\n就算佢聽話佢生性<br />\n一個唔好彩際遇差d<br />\n或者生得唔高大外型差少少<br />\n或者生不逢時<br />\n佢一生人會好撚慘<br />\n仲要未必係佢錯<br />\n做足一切<br />\n亦可以因為世道殘忍<br />\n而抹殺佢一切努力<br />\n而你作為帶佢黎世上既人<br />\n看在眼裏<br />\n怎能唔心痛<br />\n想幫亦無能為力<br />\n唔通攬住佢喊<br />\n定好似外國d老豆咁<br />\n實在唔忍心<br />\n選擇最後最無奈既一步<br />\n時間真係好快<br />\n依個世界真係冇人理你<br />\n一切自己承受"},{"pid":"a0d00f2490570b9299b675bd23e382156ff8481b","tid":2162614,"uid":65638,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T08:17:22.000Z","msg":"下，係你廢姐"},{"pid":"23bbee1db52dd8ef24d91ecd088b6143e27bf499","tid":2162614,"uid":14510,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"a0d00f2490570b9299b675bd23e382156ff8481b","tid":2162614,"uid":65638,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T08:17:22.000Z","msg":"下，係你廢姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T08:19:45.000Z","msg":"呢句真<br />\n廢人先會係到計生仔生女邊樣賺邊樣蝕"},{"pid":"ddae4bbb670c2fbfd7d60b81ad881268d1202b27","tid":2162614,"uid":103485,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T08:26:18.000Z","msg":"嗱你唔好生呀"},{"pid":"f46129c84670259bfc7ee7fa8ab76407e70c8d6c","tid":2162614,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T08:30:58.000Z","msg":"岩，生女煩少好多野"},{"pid":"b31959497ac91c1dbdf330bad6aa55bc22643511","tid":2162614,"uid":125485,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f46129c84670259bfc7ee7fa8ab76407e70c8d6c","tid":2162614,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"202